A non-committal roadmap for pepper
==================================

Planned features for 0.3:
	* API overhaul (more OOP and report-centric and report-centric)
	* repository:cat()
	* repository:log()
	* Time range arguments for all reports
	* GUI report (using lgob.gtk)

Planned for 0.3.x:
	* Bazaar backend
	* libgit2 backend
	* Meta data pre-fetching for Subversion backend

Planned features for 0.4:
	* Filter module (cloc and friends)
	* HTML module for generating custom HTML reports
	* Cache backends using "real" databases

Planned:
	* Windows version?
